data.description: Spacious, bright and airy describe this 3 Bedroom/ 4 Bathroom townhome! Professionally painted and new carpet throughout the entire home. Open floor plan with fireplace, perfect for entertaining. Spacious kitchen with island. Both front and rear-facing windows with loads of light!  Three bedrooms on one level. The primary bedroom has a walk-in closet PLUS an additional closet. Upper level laundry area. Lower level family room. Close to walking trails, shopping and restaurants. Professionally cleaned and ready to move into!
